00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,700
infinitely light,

694
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:22,960
infinitely flexible solenoid.

695
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:27,040
But,

696
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:30,760
until somebody discovers a real magnetic monopole,

