718
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:28,000
We take the solenoid infinitely long,

719
00:27:28,080 --> 00:27:30,420
we start with no current in the solenoid,

720
00:27:30,420 --> 00:27:32,140
so there's no magnetic field.

721
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:35,300
Then we start increasing the magnetic field.

