00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:36,720
Sorry,

723
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:37,480
yes.

724
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,680
We start increasing the current.

725
00:27:40,620 --> 00:27:43,640
Increasing the current creates a magnetic field

726
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,880
through the solenoid.

727
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:50,240
As we increase the current,

728
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:52,340
the magnetic field increases,

729
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:54,080
and for that reason,

730
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,880
it generates an electric field.

731
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:57,980
The electric field has a curl.

