00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,260
So it wraps around.

733
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,360
What does it wrap around?

734
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:04,040
It wraps around the solenoid.

735
00:28:06,459 --> 00:28:07,100
So,

736
00:28:07,100 --> 00:28:08,640
ramping up the current

737
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:11,200
through a solenoid

738
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:14,800
creates an electric field around the solenoid,

739
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:14,860
and it wraps around the solenoid.

740
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:15,780
And in fact,

741
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:16,380
in particular,

742
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:19,120
that electric field could accelerate a charged particle

743
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:21,240
and get it moving in a circle.

744
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,320
All right,

745
00:28:23,320 --> 00:28:24,480
that's the meaning of this equation.

746
00:28:25,860 --> 00:28:27,060
Whose law is this,

747
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,540
that a changing magnetic field makes an electric field?

748
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:30,060
I always forget.

