00:29:43,080 --> 00:29:44,740
has to wrap around something.

784
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:47,600
It wraps around the direction

785
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:50,860
of the electric field lines.

786
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:53,680
All right,

787
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:55,860
so ramping up the charge

788
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:57,040
in a capacitor

789
00:29:58,080 --> 00:30:00,480
