1463
00:53:37,400 --> 00:53:38,420
Not so.

1464
00:53:38,640 --> 00:53:41,920
And the reason is that this is anti-symmetric.

1465
00:53:42,040 --> 00:53:43,620
If you interchange mu and nu,

1466
00:53:44,560 --> 00:53:45,840
it changes sign.

1467
00:53:46,260 --> 00:53:47,300
So that means,

1468
00:53:47,300 --> 00:53:48,260
for example,

1469
00:53:48,300 --> 00:53:52,440
that F1 2 is just equal to minus F2 1.

1470
00:53:54,820 --> 00:53:57,260
