1471
00:53:57,720 --> 00:54:00,220
So the different components of F mu nu

1472
00:54:00,220 --> 00:54:01,180
are not independent.

1473
00:54:01,580 --> 00:54:02,920
It's anti-symmetric.

1474
00:54:03,380 --> 00:54:06,680
How many components of an anti-symmetric mu nu

1475
00:54:06,680 --> 00:54:09,160
