1476
00:54:09,500 --> 00:54:12,020
All the diagonal components are zero.

1477
00:54:12,160 --> 00:54:12,800
In other words,

1478
00:54:12,800 --> 00:54:13,340
if I said,

1479
00:54:13,340 --> 00:54:14,940
if nu and mu are the same,

1480
00:54:15,680 --> 00:54:17,140
