00:54:53,620 --> 00:54:54,880
You can think of it as a matrix.

1496
00:54:55,860 --> 00:54:57,660
A 4x4 matrix.

1497
00:54:57,860 --> 00:54:59,440
16 to start with.

1498
00:55:00,260 --> 00:55:01,980
Zero on the diagonal.

1499
00:55:03,320 --> 00:55:04,320
And all of them are independent.

1500
00:55:04,340 --> 00:55:05,160
The off-diagonal,

1501
00:55:06,320 --> 00:55:07,860
the off-diagonal,

1502
00:55:07,860 --> 00:55:11,000
there are six off-diagonal

